                    <p><div class="content_para"><p>Available from the <a href="/web/20180712204044/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=50066&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.sts.org%2fsites%2fdefault%2ffiles%2fdocuments%2fpdf%2fguidelines%2fGuidelines_CPB%2520Temperature%2520Management.pdf" title="Society of Thoracic Surgeons Web site">Society of Thoracic Surgeons Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180712204044im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </p></div></p>
